      <title>瑞士财政部长驳斥瑞银反对增加资本的游说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/swiss-finance-minister-rebuffs-ubs-lobbying-against-more-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士财政部长卡琳·凯勒-苏特 (Karin Keller-Sutter) 明确表示，瑞银集团 (UBS Group AG) 目前针对新资本要求的游说活动不会动摇她的观点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/swiss-finance-minister-rebuffs-ubs-lobbying-against-more-capital</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 09:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼电力公司欠孟加拉国 8 亿美元欠款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/adani-power-has-800-million-in-unpaid-dues-from-bangladesh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的发电部门已经从孟加拉国收取了高达 8 亿美元的未缴会费，该国持续数周的暴力抗议活动造成数百人死亡，并迫使上届政府于本月下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/adani-power-has-800-million-in-unpaid-dues-from-bangladesh</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 09:11:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳打破可可产业外国融资传统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/ghana-breaks-foreign-funding-tradition-for-cocoa-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[32 年后，加纳不再从国际银行借款来资助下一季的可可作物。彭博社首席非洲通讯员 Jennifer Zabasajja 详细介绍了这一变化对加纳经济的意义。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/ghana-breaks-foreign-funding-tradition-for-cocoa-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 09:00:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰克逊霍尔会议历史表明鲍威尔避开了市场冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/jackson-hole-history-points-to-powell-sidestepping-market-shocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果美国财政部和美国股市对杰罗姆·鲍威尔周五在杰克逊霍尔研讨会上的表现有信心的话，那就是：他会谨慎行事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/jackson-hole-history-points-to-powell-sidestepping-market-shocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Capitec 的全球扩张计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/capitec-s-global-expansion-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非 Capitec 的股价在过去 12 个月中飙升，成为非洲大陆增长最快的银行。首席执行官 Gerrie Fourie 向彭博社首席非洲通讯员 Jennifer Zabasajja 独家讲述了成功背后的原因。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/capitec-s-global-expansion-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 08:51:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CVC 和 DSV 分别向 DB Schenker 提交了 140 亿欧元的竞标报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/cvc-dsv-said-to-submit-14-billion-bids-for-db-schenker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，丹麦运输集团 DSV A/S 和 CVC Capital Partners Plc 牵头的财团分别提出了具有约束力的投标，对德国铁路物流部门的估值约为 140 亿欧元（156 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/cvc-dsv-said-to-submit-14-billion-bids-for-db-schenker</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 08:16:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储讲话或为利率提供线索，黄金反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/gold-xauusd-holds-decline-before-fed-speech-that-may-offer-rate-clues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔发表讲话，可能为央行的货币政策路径提供新的线索，在此之前，金价反弹至每盎司 2,500 美元以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/gold-xauusd-holds-decline-before-fed-speech-that-may-offer-rate-clues</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 00:29:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员等待鲍威尔关于利率前景的线索，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国联邦储备委员会主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔 (Jerome Powell) 发表杰克逊霍尔讲话之前，油价上涨，收复了部分周跌幅，该讲话将为美国利率走势提供线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 23:28:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔讲话前股市上涨；日元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在杰罗姆鲍威尔发表杰克逊霍尔讲话之前，股市小幅走高，交易员们猜测美联储主席是否会为降息打开大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 22:31:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场复苏带动业绩回升，平安利润上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/ping-an-profit-rises-as-market-recovery-bolsters-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[平安保险（集团）股份有限公司 (Ping An Insurance (Group) Co.) 宣布，上半年利润增长近 7%，股市复苏提振了这家中国市值第二大保险公司的投资回报。该公司股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/ping-an-profit-rises-as-market-recovery-bolsters-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 10:03:28 GMT</pubDate>
